results.name: First occurrence of exponent n in A080121 corresponding to the minimum prime of the form (k^(2^n) + (k+1)^(2^n)) = A122900(k).
comment: Minimum primes of the form n^(2^m) + (n+1)^(2^m) are listed in A122900. The exponents m are listed in A080121.
